highest migration multiplier.

01:10:30.540 --> 01:10:34.410
So it's the multiplier
through those two categories

01:10:34.410 --> 01:10:36.590
that actually generated
that huge spurt

01:10:36.590 --> 01:10:38.640
and then it could continue
to multiply.

01:10:38.640 --> 01:10:40.790
Add to that other events
like Tiananmen Square

01:10:40.790 --> 01:10:43.650
where we make exceptions and
we bring in a few extra here

01:10:43.650 --> 01:10:47.450
and a few extra there, and
you have a huge potential.

01:10:47.450 --> 01:10:49.070
And that's what's happened
with the Asian complex.

01:10:49.070 --> 01:10:50.370
&gt;&gt; Ruth Wasem: Yeah,
