01:11:13.970 --> 01:11:15.270
They couldn't get out.

01:11:15.270 --> 01:11:17.040
&gt;&gt; Yep. That's exactly right.

01:11:17.040 --> 01:11:20.300
&gt;&gt; Ruth Wasem: And so going
